370
00:23:39,220 --> 00:23:40,860
The Love Broker 3.0,

371
00:23:40,860 --> 00:23:42,590
the Shining Warm-Winter Pact

372
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:43,430
has started, right?

373
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:47,070
How far has the team gotten

374
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:48,190
in test packaging the update?

375
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:49,430
We're all ready, Mr. Jiang.

376
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:50,310
Still, at the moment,

377
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:52,220
Walter Games is going
to purchase HC Interactive.

378
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:54,550
Should we push back the patch date?

379
00:23:54,550 --> 00:23:55,710
We haven't announced it anyway.

380
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:57,190
What do you mean?

381
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:59,470
A major update to the game

382
00:23:59,470 --> 00:24:00,980
will lead to a drastic increase
in profits.

383
00:24:01,710 --> 00:24:03,380
If we give the profits

384
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:05,140
to Walter Games as a welcoming gift,

385
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:06,190
