389
00:24:39,340 --> 00:24:40,340
Make yourself at home.

390
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:48,910
Mr. Gu.

391
00:24:49,950 --> 00:24:51,980
Isn't it very interesting?

392
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:54,430
You insisted on going to HC Game before.

393
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:56,470
But after all that fuss,

394
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:58,470
Walter Games end up buying over HC Game.

395
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,740
I'll get to the point.

396
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:03,620
After you purchase HC Game,

397
00:25:03,620 --> 00:25:05,190
what are your plans for Hero's Path?

398
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:09,590
I don't like it when you say that.

399
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,310
I'll be honest.

400
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,950
We want to buy HC Game

401
00:25:24,950 --> 00:25:26,980
mainly because we like you.

402
00:25:29,140 --> 00:25:31,380
So, what will happen
to Hero's Path in the future

403
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:32,620
is still your decision.

404
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:33,550
Still, we think

405
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,380
that there are many elements in the game

406
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:37,550
that can be swapped out.

407
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:41,830
For example?

408
00:25:42,860 --> 00:25:43,980
For example,

409
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:45,950
Lin, that NPC at the start.

410
00:25:45,950 --> 00:25:48,590
We don't think it's good
for him to hold a conch.

411
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:51,550
It should be changed
to a magic staff or tome.

412
00:25:51,550 --> 00:25:53,550
Also, the main character
isn't well-designed.

413
00:25:53,550 --> 00:25:54,470
We want the main character

414
00:25:54,470 --> 00:25:55,710
to not belong to any factions

415
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:56,950
and be a wandering hero.

416
00:25:56,950 --> 00:25:58,340
That needs to be changed.

417
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:05,310
Of course,

418
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:06,670
how the change happens

419
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:09,220
still depends on you.

420
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:18,740
If the one you want is me

421
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:19,910
and this game,

422
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:22,340
don't you think
you're going through a lot of trouble

423
00:26:22,740 --> 00:26:24,830
by buying over HC Game?

424
00:26:24,830 --> 00:26:25,860
We have no choice.

425
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:28,100
You're too hard to hire.

426
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,620
Our boss thinks
you're a little too quirky.

427
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:31,340
We failed to hire you twice.

428
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,910
So we decided to just buy HC Game

429
00:26:32,910 --> 00:26:34,190
and be your boss.

430
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,950
Actually, you could have bought me over.

431
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:42,310
However,

432
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:44,100
that depends
on how much you're willing to pay.

433
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,670
Why the sudden change of mind, Mr. Gu?

434
00:26:51,590 --> 00:26:53,510
What's really important to me is

435
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:55,030
to finish the game.

436
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:57,920
As for who invested in it and how much,

437
00:26:58,550 --> 00:26:59,860
I see no big difference.

438
00:27:00,340 --> 00:27:01,130
It's all negotiable.

439
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:03,910
All negotiable.

440
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:06,980
I only have one request.

441
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:07,980
