442
00:27:10,100 --> 00:27:12,310
I signed a non-compete agreement
when I was hired.

443
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:14,260
If I have to leave halfway through,

444
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:16,620
I'll have to pay back
all expenses incurred.

445
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:17,380
When I joined them,

446
00:27:17,380 --> 00:27:19,260
I was very unhappy with the agreement.

447
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:21,310
Still, I had to sign it

448
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,190
to create the game.

449
00:27:22,190 --> 00:27:23,070
Walter Games can

450
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,470
pay your breakup fee.

451
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:29,590
I have another request.

452
00:27:30,790 --> 00:27:32,260
I need a profit share clause.

453
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:38,070
Even so,

454
00:27:38,070 --> 00:27:39,670
the total cost of purchasing me

455
00:27:39,670 --> 00:27:42,340
is only 10% of buying HC Game.

456
00:27:43,590 --> 00:27:44,670
It's a great deal.

457
00:27:51,340 --> 00:27:52,740
In that case,

458
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:53,860
we can retract the notice

459
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:55,740
for purchasing HC Game.

460
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:57,670
Wise move.

461
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:00,380
Very well.

462
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:01,260
List out the names

463
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:02,740
of those you'll be bringing over.

464
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:18,500
I've misjudged you.

465
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:22,190
All this time,
HC Game fully supported you.

466
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,910
Now that we're in trouble,

467
00:28:24,910 --> 00:28:26,550
you're the first to jump ship.

468
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:30,910
My goal has always been
to finish the game.

469
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:32,430
The finances, connections,
and manpower of Walter Games

470
00:28:32,430 --> 00:28:33,540
are greater than HC Game's.

471
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:36,000
If Walter Games
can give me a better deal,

472
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:37,720
why won't I go?

473
00:28:38,620 --> 00:28:40,100
You're too selfish!

474
00:28:41,670 --> 00:28:42,950
I've always supported you,

475
00:28:42,950 --> 00:28:44,590
backing up the 9th Business Unit

476
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:46,590
and fighting to give you more time
and resources.

477
00:28:47,020 --> 00:28:48,430
How could you do this to me?

478
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:50,670
How can you do this to the team?

479
00:28:50,950 --> 00:28:52,470
How can you do this to your dream?

480
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:54,550
What you're doing...

481
00:28:54,550 --> 00:28:57,550
I think there might
be a misunderstanding.

482
00:28:57,910 --> 00:28:59,470
Mr. Gu is not that kind of man.

483
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:00,980
Indeed.

484
00:29:01,470 --> 00:29:04,380
Even if he just wants
to complete the game,

485
00:29:05,590 --> 00:29:07,470
I think it's a little extreme.

486
00:29:07,860 --> 00:29:09,310
Don't jump to conclusions.

487
00:29:09,710 --> 00:29:10,790
Let's wait.

488
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,190
Gu Xun,

489
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:18,910
I always thought we were true partners.

490
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:25,220
I'm doing all of this for Hero's Path.

491
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:26,950
I've already made up my mind.

492
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,220
This is just a notice.

493
00:29:39,710 --> 00:29:40,710
Fine.

494
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,430
I have an announcement to make.

495
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:02,140
I've decided
to bring the 9th Business Unit

496
00:30:02,140 --> 00:30:03,190
and Hero's Path

497
00:30:03,740 --> 00:30:04,980
