of the game to Western.

521
00:31:36,340 --> 00:31:37,670
I just can't accept it.

522
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:41,910
Those who are capable can go anywhere.

523
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:44,100
I won't go to Walter Games.

524
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:45,220
She's right.

525
00:31:46,380 --> 00:31:47,620
Before this...

526
00:31:47,620 --> 00:31:48,280
Yes,

527
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:49,930
I was here for Mr. Gu.

528
00:31:50,710 --> 00:31:51,820
The heart of the team has changed now.

529
00:31:52,710 --> 00:31:54,860
The 9th Business Unit
is not what it was before.

530
00:31:58,950 --> 00:31:59,710
Boss,

531
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:02,070
are you going with Mr. Gu?

532
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:08,950
While I don't quite agree
with Mr. Gu's decision,

533
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:11,220
this one time

534
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:11,950
is the last chance

535
00:32:11,950 --> 00:32:13,500
I'm giving myself
to make a Triple-A game.

536
00:32:14,100 --> 00:32:15,260
As long as we can complete it,

537
00:32:15,670 --> 00:32:16,950
